sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as ChuSoHuuTaiLieu
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant DocSvc as DocumentService
participant DocDb as Mongo_Document
participant Webhook as WebhookService

Note over User,Webhook: Chặng 1 - Tạo tài liệu và versioning
User->>Client: Tạo metadata tài liệu
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/documents
Gateway->>DocSvc: Forward
DocSvc->>DocDb: Insert document
DocSvc->>Webhook: Publish document.created
DocSvc-->>Client: 201

User->>Client: Upload phiên bản mới
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/documents/:id/versions
Gateway->>DocSvc: Forward
DocSvc->>DocDb: Push previousVersions + set currentVersion
DocSvc-->>Client: 200
